This request for a preliminary ruling concerns the interpretation of Articles 49, 52 and 56 TFEU, and of Directive 2005/36/EC of the European Parliament and of the Council of 7 September 2005 on the recognition of professional qualifications (
OJ 2005 L 255, p. 22
), as amended by Directive 2013/55/EU of the European Parliament and of the Council of 20 November 2013 (
OJ 2013 L 354, p. 132
) (‘Directive 2005/36’).
